name: LMS Feasibility Partner
query:
SELECT
    lfp.supplier AS "Supplier:Link/Supplier:200",
    lfp.class AS "Class:Data:120",
    lfp.status AS "Status:Data:150",
    lfp.supplier_group AS "Supplier Group:Link/Supplier Group:150",
    lfp.address_1 AS "Address Line 1:Data:200",
    lfp.address_2 AS "Address Line 2:Data:200",
    lfp.city AS "City:Data:130",
    lfp.state AS "State:Data:130",
    lfp.pincode AS "Pincode:Data:100",
    lfp.primary_contact AS "Primary Contact:Data:200"
FROM
    `tabLMS Feasibility Partner` lfp
WHERE
    lfp.active = 1     -- ✅ Only Active Partners
ORDER BY
    lfp.supplier ASC;
